commit message:
Minor updates.

Changed variable names and updated a some comments.
Also, removed some printouts.
Prepare for baud rate in service.
Moved hard coded text strings to resources.

Simplify SenderThread.

The sending application should not send to big data chunks.
Use proper name for member variables.
Move class ByteArray to separate file.
Increase width of icons to comply with Android icon design.
Use switch statement instead of if when checking product id.
Rename Arduino Uno R3 product id define.
Add log message when finding Arduino device.
Show device name of found device.
Check for null when opening device.

Add support for Arduino Mega 2560 ADK.

Thanks to Jose Miguel Hernandez Paredes.
